b. 2<sup>3</sup> x111.1111 = 1.111111 x  2<sup>5</sup>   
c. 2<sup>-2</sup> x101.110011 =1.01110011 x 2<sup>0</sup>   
d. 2<sup>-5</sup>x101101.00000110011000 = 1.0110100000110011000 x 2<sup>0</sup>  

